Shannon grew up in Buckaroo, Oregon, a little town with an unusual high percentage of serial killers called the Buckaroo Butchers. Shannon's prom date was Edward Warren, before he became the Nailbiter.

Shannon later became the sheriff of Buckaroo.

deck: Serial killer from Buckaroo, Oregon.
description:
Origin

Mocked for his inability to read or write, Norman Woods went on a murder spree, burning down libraries all over Washington and Idaho. Sometimes with people still inside. Dubbed the Book Burner, he was the first of the Buckaroo Butchers. In the 70s, the Book Burner started killing authors.

His grandson, Raleigh Woods, owns world's first serial killer souvenir shop, named Murder Store.
